Add light, consistent metadata to improve retrieval quality: - title (e.g., “Resistor”)
- type (equipment | instrument | machine | symbol)
- function (one line)
- connections (series/parallel/NA)
- ideal_properties (e.g., ammeter: ~0 Ω, voltmeter: very high Ω)
- image_photo_path
- image_symbol_path
- aliases (e.g., rheostat ↔ variable resistor; auto‑transformer ↔ autotransformer)
- page_source (story1 | story2 | story3 | story4)
- tags (e.g., measurement, protection, motor, passive‑component)
