•	Keep the directory name images/ to preserve existing paths; this helps if you later re‑host the images.

•	For files with spacing or capitalization (e.g., DC Motor.png, Rehostate.png), either normalize (rename) and record an alias, or keep as‑is and ensure the exact path is indexed.

•	Remove HTML/JS; only store clean markdown/text + image references for embeddings.

•	Consider generating two embeddings per item: one from the full description and one from the concise one‑liner.
